cmake-tutorials 记录 cmake的常见构建方式

参考
    https://cmake.org/cmake/help/git-stage/guide/tutorial/index.html
    https://github.com/Kitware/CMake/tree/master/Help/guide/tutorial



在cmake项目目录时，常用命令:
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ../
    cmake --build .
安装命令:
    cmake --install .
    cmake --install . --prefix "/home/myuser/installdir"
测试命令:
    ctest -N
    ctest -VV
    ctest -C Debug -VV
    ctest -C Release -VV

Step1: without cmake
Step2: basic
Step3: add a library
Step4: add a library
Step5: install and test
    测试命令:
        cd Step5
        mkdir build
        cmake ..
        cmake --build .
        ctest
        ctest -N
        ctest -VV
    验证安装命令:
        cmake --install . --prefix "/home/myuser/installdir"
Step6: add System Introspection
Step7: a Custom Command and Generated File
Step8: Packaging an Installer
    命令: cd Step8
         mkdir build
         cd build
         cmake ..
         cpack
         cpack -G ZIP -C Debug
         cpack --config CPackSourceConfig.cmake
Step9:  Packaging an Installer
Step10: Selecting Static or Shared Libraries
Step11: Adding Generator Expressions
Step12: Adding Export Configuration
    cd Step12
    mkdir debug
    mkdir release
    cd debug
    cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug ..
    cmake --build .
    cd ../release
    cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
    cmake --build .
    cpack --config MultiCPackConfig.cmake

